HEADWORD: lien
<hw>lien</hw>, etc. }</mhw>
<fld>(Law)</fld> <def>A charge, lien, etc., that successively attaches
to such assets as a person may have from time to time, leaving him more
or less free to dispose of or encumber them as if no such charge or lien
existed.</def></p>

<p><ent>Floatingly</ent>⟦br⟧
